4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge in the field. This 16-week program covers essential skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Students will learn data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards, including ISO 27001 and NIST. The bootcamp features three live online classes per week with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Courses are available in English or Spanish.

